    "The proposed rear dormer window would, by reason of its bulk, scale and mass, appear out of scale and character with the dwelling and materially harmful to the visual amenity of the surrounding area contrary to Policies 7 and 26 of the Havering Local Plan and the Residential Extensions and Alterations Supplementary Planning Document.",
